#. Description of the plugin
#: wp-headless.php
msgid "Turn any properly-built WordPress theme into a React headless frontend. The plugin engages headless mode when the active theme ships dist/index.html, serving the SPA with a full runtime payload, asset proxy, and REST primitives for every URL kind WordPress can route to."
msgstr ""

